OL,3,CElectric charging points could become
OL,4,Cmandatory for all new homes in Wales
OL,6,FElectric charging points could be made
OL,7,Fa mandatory requirement outside all
OL,8,Fnew homes in Wales.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government is consulting on
OL,11,Fproposals to mandate the installation
OL,12,Fof electric vehicle charge-points in
OL,13,Fall new residential and non-
OL,14,Fresidential buildings where car
OL,15,Fparking is available.
OL,17,FThe proposed regulations would require
OL,18,Fall new homes with an associated car
OL,19,Fparking space, including properties
OL,20,Fbeing redeveloped or changing use, to
OL,21,Finstal electric charging points.
