OL,3,CElectric charging points could become
OL,4,Cmandatory for all new homes in Wales
OL,6,FNew non-residential buildings, and
OL,7,Fthose undergoing major renovation,
OL,8,Fwith more than 10 car parking spaces
OL,9,Fwould need a charge point, as well as
OL,10,Fcable routes for an electric vehicle
OL,11,Fcharge point for every one in five
OL,12,Fspaces.
OL,14,FIt comes as the Welsh Government moves
OL,15,Ftowards net zero.
