OL,3,CElectric charging points could become
OL,4,Cmandatory for all new homes in Wales
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has already
OL,7,Fannounced proposals to ban the sale of
OL,8,Fnew petrol and diesel-only cars and
OL,9,Fvans in 2030. This will inevitably
OL,10,Fincrease the demand on electric
OL,11,Fcharging points.
OL,13,FWelsh socio-economic data provided by
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Government suggests there
OL,15,Fwill be a need for 30,000 to 55,000
OL,16,Ffast chargers to be available in Wales
OL,17,Fby 2030.
OL,19,FThe consultation is encouraging people
OL,20,Fto share their views about the
OL,21,Fproposals by 29 November.
